  "A fireworks designer wants to create a brilliant blue color in a pyrotechnic display. She knows that copper compounds produce blue-green light. The light emitted corresponds to specific electronic transitions in copper atoms. If she wanted a higher-energy (shorter wavelength) blue light, what type of electron transition would be needed?": "",
